title: Coaster, ca. 1810
dimensions: H x diam.: 4.7 x 15.2 cm (1 7/8 x 6 in.)
description: Round with low straight sides, horizontal rim top edge with egg and dart molding, stepped at base; turned wooden base with concentric grooves and central silver boss.

tombstone.epitaph:
Coaster, ca. 1810.
ca. 1810. copper, silver, wood. Bequest of Walter Phelps Warren. 1986-61-9.
